{"id":305854,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/维权网-杭州维权人士陈美佳要求报销医药费被村/","date":"2013-07-27T09:03:19Z","modified":"2013-07-27T09:03:19Z","title":"维权网 | 杭州维权人士陈美佳要求报销医药费被村书记抬出办公室（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员陆冲冠报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>点</span><span>，杭州市江干区彭埠镇普福社区访民陈美佳柱着拐杖到村委会办公大楼找社区党委书记杨月根，要求报销她在北京上访被政府截访押回杭州途中摔伤治疗的两万多元医药费。杨月根不仅不答应，反而破口大骂，叫几个联防队员将陈美佳抬出办公室。这些男性粗野地在衣着单薄的陈美佳身上乱抓，陈美佳正色地说：“我的身体属我丈夫专有，你们可以随便乱碰吗？杨书记叫你们杀人你们也去杀人吗？”尚有羞耻感的联防队员只好停下来。于是杨月根又叫村妇女主任陈国娟带了四个女人将陈美佳抬出办公室，扔到村委会办公楼二楼大厅。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>陈美佳</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>从北京被押回，在济南洗手间试图逃跑时被截访人员追赶摔伤，回家后在浙江富阳骨科医院治疗了一个半月，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日</span><span>出院回到家里。陈美佳在住院期间花去医疗费两万多元，她认为应由政府承担责任，因为她受伤是由政府非法截访引起的，但镇里的书记和镇长见了她就逃，她只好找村里，但党委书记杨月根居然命人将仍然拄着双拐走路的陈美佳抬到二楼大厅，并关掉空调，将她在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>度的高温下“蒸馒头”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>自</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日</span><span>以来，陈美佳为了讨回公道，在村办公大楼“公开、公平、公正”的招牌下已睡了三个晚上。今天是第四个晚上，村干部们或者正在“麻战”，或者已进入梦乡，但无助的冤妇陈美佳正一个人睡在蒸笼般的村办公大楼里受煎熬。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>杨月根被官媒称为“感动江干——十佳道德模范”，然而这样一个“道德模范”，却将一位因上访而受重伤的冤妇抬出办公室“清蒸”，真是玷污了“道德”这两个汉字。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>杨月根电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13605809881</span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><span>陈美佳电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13083987824</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-fSEZ5HirivA/UfM4JIIoXqI/AAAAAAAAl6w/usmQMqto7Cs/s1600/gg_%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"221\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-fSEZ5HirivA/UfM4JIIoXqI/AAAAAAAAl6w/usmQMqto7Cs/s320/gg_%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-V_MkN4udeLM/UfM4LNuxpOI/AAAAAAAAl64/3_I3epirF8Q/s1600/hh_%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"252\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-V_MkN4udeLM/UfM4LNuxpOI/AAAAAAAAl64/3_I3epirF8Q/s320/hh_%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-QGoAFsSOaBc/UfM4No-eUBI/AAAAAAAAl7E/0GO_DC4jEEk/s1600/%25E6%259C%258B_%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"236\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-QGoAFsSOaBc/UfM4No-eUBI/AAAAAAAAl7E/0GO_DC4jEEk/s320/%25E6%259C%258B_%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-pdRhlU14Jn0/UfM4NzhsmqI/AAAAAAAAl7I/C_xuvPk_EFg/s1600/%25E6%258A%2598_%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"184\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-pdRhlU14Jn0/UfM4NzhsmqI/AAAAAAAAl7I/C_xuvPk_EFg/s320/%25E6%258A%2598_%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,205